    "text": "🐍 Join me at EuroPython Beginners' Day Unconference! 🚀\n\nI'm excited to be co-organizing the EuroPython Beginners' Day Unconference with Honza Javorek on July 19th in Prague! This event is perfect for juniors and career changers looking to break into tech. It's a part of EuroPython and its Sprints weekend.\n\nWhat to expect:\n- Panel discussions with junior devs and hiring managers\n- An interactive workshop for your first tech job\n- Discussion circles connecting beginners with pros\n- Lightning talks from recent career changers\n\nOnly 40 spots available! Applications close May 11th.\nFree for EuroPython ticket holders, €5 otherwise.\nKnow someone who could benefit? Please share! Sign up through the form (link in comments).\n\n#EuroPython #CareerChange #TechCareers #PythonCommunity #BeginnerFriendly",
